title: List of provincial parks in Ontario
text: The list of provincial parks in the Canadian province of <a href="Ontario">Ontario</a> contains lists of more than 300 provincial parks in <a href="Ontario">Ontario</a>. These provincial parks are maintained by <a href="Ontario%20Parks">Ontario Parks</a>. For a list of protected areas in Ontario, see the <a href="List%20of%20protected%20areas%20of%20Ontario">List of protected areas of Ontario</a>.
